{"tid":582814,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PS4]Monster Hunter World 弓討論區 [3]","createTime":"2018-03-06T13:05:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T06:26:42.000Z","uid":28974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e5daba1511c958aba90c9a6b665682387a36efcc","tid":582814,"uid":28974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T13:05:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong>弓介紹</strong><br />\n據聞係MHW入面改動最大嘅武器，基本上除咗曲射仲係屎之外冇樣野同前作一樣<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">連射</span>／<span style=\"color: green;\">擴散</span>／<span style=\"color: blue;\">貫通矢</span>（重射：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）被重新分配至唔同動作，令到邊把弓都對應到近中遠三種距離，擁有全武器中最高的柔韌性[url][/url]<br />\n<br />\n<strong>主流戰法</strong><br />\n因為弓仲係開荒期，就算係TA片玩法都可以好多種<br />\n簡單講下目前dps最高嘅三種戰法：<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">1）龍之一矢中心<br />\n不停loop龍之一矢<br />\n參考：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Lgx7_VrT3Dg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLgx7_VrT3Dg&d=FkRYAJ%2BVlyd61e66YX%2B9U%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=99d0cb6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Lgx7_VrT3Dg</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">2）剛射中心<br />\n需要開放叉4（弓溜め階段解放），R2射到叉4後再接剛射，charge step以上重複<br />\n參考：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9zrIZwU4im0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9zrIZwU4im0&d=FkRYAJ%2BVlyd61e66YX%2B9U%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=93767c18\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9zrIZwU4im0</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LTkTAAN7DZo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLTkTAAN7DZo&d=FkRYAJ%2BVlyd61e66YX%2B9U%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=0cc8fb9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LTkTAAN7DZo</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">3）跳躍攻擊(壁撃ち)中心<br />\n向特定地形charge step會出到跳躍攻擊，高傷但未必場場用到<br />\n參考：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5HE4ZIAUhPE&amp;t=1s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5HE4ZIAUhPE%26t%3D1s&d=FkRYAJ%2BVlyd61e66YX%2B9U%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=5aaf4188\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5HE4ZIAUhPE&amp;t=1s</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>連段介紹</strong><br />\n個Post唔沈底先算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>Link</strong><br />\n部分可能outdate咗所以睇下就算<br />\n<br />\n介紹：<br />\n（中）<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=5786&amp;snA=135041\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D5786%26snA%3D135041&d=FkRYAJ%2BVlyd61e66YX%2B9U%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=9a5f314a\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=5786&amp;snA=135041</a><br />\n（日）<a href=\"http://kisha-poppou.com/mhw-bow/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkisha-poppou.com%2Fmhw-bow%2F&d=FkRYAJ%2BVlyd61e66YX%2B9U%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=1721ce10\" target=\"_blank\">http://kisha-poppou.com/mhw-bow/</a><br />\n<br />\nChannel推薦：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCWinJaYAlxI9LjGmFofiuwg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCWinJaYAlxI9LjGmFofiuwg&d=FkRYAJ%2BVlyd61e66YX%2B9U%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=e18f92d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCWinJaYAlxI9LjGmFofiuwg</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCYKxxq2Px3t_dPXtLcT0ZKQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCYKxxq2Px3t_dPXtLcT0ZKQ&d=FkRYAJ%2BVlyd61e66YX%2B9U%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=c88cb99d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCYKxxq2Px3t_dPXtLcT0ZKQ</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好比佢沈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"941315eca2b23624160e2ca25b4ab6bd3c3a3575","tid":582814,"uid":28974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"